text: Soyeon: ..My fever went up to 39.8 degrees celsius????
Soyeon: Am I going to die??
Soyeon: I can't believe that I also got a new team project right after I finished the report of that physics experiment...
Soyeon: I heard that the new team project members are announced in today's class...
Soyeon: Everyone except me would have met each other today huh?
Soyeon: Honestly it's quite exhausting to talk to team project members, so isn't it damn good to be able to skip it?
Soyeon:  Seriously I can't go out in this condition given the pandemic...
Soyeon: Wait... what if I really caught the "disease"?
Soyeon: It would be fucking great to enjoy the holidays after being sick for a few days yeah?
Soyeon: I need to take a test while getting a prescription.
Soyeon: Haah... I love free holidays but don't want to pick my nose...
Soyeon: The clinic will be closed soon, so I have to hurry.
Soyeon: I wasted too much time writing the physics report...
Soyeon: It's too cold to go out without a varsity jacket these days.
Soyeon: Do you think I would go out in pajama pants even if I'm an unpopular shit?
Soyeon: I'm not sure if sombody would call me... but who knows.
Soyeon: I need my wallet to pay for the medical fee.
